  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>&gt;<a class=\"entity-link\" data-pack=\"sfrpg.class-features\" data-id=\"cA0NuGh484BwlDjX\" draggable=\"true\"><i class=\"fas fa-suitcase\"></i> Drone</a></p>\n        <p>As a move action, you can directly control your drone. This allows the drone to take both a move action and any standard action this turn (one from your control, and one from its limited AI). If you also take a swift action, your drone can take a swift action as well, or it can combine its actions into a full action. Your drone must be able to see or hear you, or be within range of your custom rig, for you to directly control your drone.</p>",
